01:04:25.775 --> 01:04:30.310
- Sure, the question is will
we talk about climate change

01:04:30.310 --> 01:04:31.143
on the vineyards.

01:04:31.143 --> 01:04:34.740
I think nobody knows
exactly what's gonna happen.

01:04:34.740 --> 01:04:38.857
But as the climate warms up,

01:04:38.857 --> 01:04:43.580
that diurnal difference between
